{"tid":2373114,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【金正恩都屈】「A貨金正恩」稱遭警屈藏彈藥需定時報到 質疑因諷刺中共被警針對「任意拘捕」","createTime":"2021-01-20T08:16:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T09:36:25.000Z","uid":378134,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f9f50f7ea9289231e18f324b32ff2b7267a64120","tid":2373114,"uid":378134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T08:16:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210120/2HWBK25YYNCEJAQAE2B5XTOTAE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210120%2F2HWBK25YYNCEJAQAE2B5XTOTAE%2F&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia1tf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=712ba441\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210120%2F2HWBK25YYNCEJAQAE2B5XTOTAE%2F&h=43dd1bc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210120/2HWBK25YYNCEJAQAE2B5XTOTAE/</a><br />\n<br />\n經常以北韓領導人金正恩打扮參與遊行的居港澳洲籍「A貨金正恩」Howard X ，今（20日）在其Facebook專頁發聲明指，去年10月28日遭約10名警察上門搜屋，並以涉嫌無牌管有彈藥將他拘捕，當中涉及BB彈槍；他至今仍未被起訴，但需每6星期到警署報到。他質疑，警方是針對他對中共政府的諷刺，作出的「an arbitrary arrest （任意拘捕）」。<br />\n<br />\nHoward曾向當時的警方質疑，其拘捕行動是毫無根據，但警方強調命令是來自更高級的部門（the order came from another department higher up），他們只是工作。Howard 又稱，警方曾提到他去年多次出現在遊行或公眾活動現場，例如7.1遊行以及10.1遊行當日他都有出現在IFC，令懷疑這次拘捕根本不是因為BB彈槍。<br />\n<br />\nHoward認為，其拘捕是由於他過去對中共政府的諷刺性批評，繼而作出的「an arbitrary arrest （任意拘捕）」；續指拘捕不僅為了騷擾他，亦藉此竊取他的指紋及搜屋。他重申，自己尚未被起訴，但需每6星期到警署報到。<br />\n<br />\n會唔會屈埋佢粒充氣核彈係毀滅性武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8100e08ca2cf2461899e71cc0bd362c33718b1cd","tid":2373114,"uid":14782,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T08:20:17.000Z","msg":"去年10月28日遭約10名警察上門搜屋，並以涉嫌無牌管有彈藥將他拘捕，當中涉及BB彈槍<br />\n<br />\n我有無睇錯？<br />\n唔係屈管有槍械，屈管有彈藥？？？"},{"pid":"c26641568d0a0a4cebc9ce3d8a51306c2d94a3dc","tid":2373114,"uid":145496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T08:22:36.000Z","msg":"仲以為係肥蔡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5886b43446e728b153d9242aa30dd62593694918","tid":2373114,"uid":165749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8100e08ca2cf2461899e71cc0bd362c33718b1cd","tid":2373114,"uid":14782,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T08:20:17.000Z","msg":"去年10月28日遭約10名警察上門搜屋，並以涉嫌無牌管有彈藥將他拘捕，當中涉及BB彈槍<br />\n<br />\n我有無睇錯？<br />\n唔係屈管有槍械，屈管有彈藥？？？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T08:22:41.000Z","msg":"咁咪應該封哂啲賣玩具槍既舖頭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ca0e58b1dfb36d80afb7541c8a1408e5753d0f8","tid":2373114,"uid":50502,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T08:24:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/915ABa2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F915ABa2.png&h=7abfa2d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依枝？"},{"pid":"3b3855b8dc912ddc296ce1aba83c295bec7b22c4","tid":2373114,"uid":36791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ca0e58b1dfb36d80afb7541c8a1408e5753d0f8","tid":2373114,"uid":50502,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T08:24:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/915ABa2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F915ABa2.png&h=7abfa2d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依枝？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T08:25:06.000Z","msg":"係幾似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a85ff531c3d197e550643462503ca9973e518779","tid":2373114,"uid":14782,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"5886b43446e728b153d9242aa30dd62593694918","tid":2373114,"uid":165749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8100e08ca2cf2461899e71cc0bd362c33718b1cd","tid":2373114,"uid":14782,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T08:20:17.000Z","msg":"去年10月28日遭約10名警察上門搜屋，並以涉嫌無牌管有彈藥將他拘捕，當中涉及BB彈槍<br />\n<br />\n我有無睇錯？<br />\n唔係屈管有槍械，屈管有彈藥？？